building_construction_sector_lvl = {
	value = 0
	every_scope_building = {
		limit = {
			is_building_type = building_construction_sector
		}
		add = level
	}
}
building_urban_center_lvl = {
	value = 0
	every_scope_building = {
		limit = {
			is_building_type = building_urban_center
		}
		add = level
	}
}

building_urban_center_lvl_by_base_rate = {
	value = building_urban_center_lvl
	multiply = {
		value = {
		 	add = 10
		 	subtract = owner.base_rate_percentage_decimal
		}
		divide = 9
	}
	max = building_urban_center_lvl
	min = 1
	round = yes
}

base_rate_for_je_max_construction_lvl = {
	value = 10
	subtract = base_rate_percentage_decimal
	multiply = 10
}

building_ef_private_construction_max_level_var = {
	value = var:gdp_view_fc
	divide = 10
	multiply = {
		value = {
		 	add = 10
		 	subtract = base_rate_percentage_decimal
		}
		divide = 9
	}

	min = 1
	round = yes
}

building_ef_private_construction_lvl_state = {
	value = b:building_ef_private_construction.level
}

building_ef_private_construction_lvl = {
	value = 0
	every_scope_building = {
		limit = {
			is_building_type = building_ef_private_construction
		}
		add = level
	}
}
building_ef_private_construction_lvl_to_build = {
	value = building_urban_center_lvl #building_construction_sector_lvl

	multiply = {
		value = {
		 	add = 10
		 	subtract = owner.base_rate_percentage_decimal
		}
		divide = 9
	}
	subtract = building_ef_private_construction_lvl

	max = building_urban_center_lvl
	min = 0
	round = yes
}
bg_gold_mining_potential_lvl_to_build = {
	every_scope_state = {
		limit = {
			has_potential_resource = bg_gold_mining
		}
		add = 1
	}
}
state_infrastructure = {
	value = 0
	add = infrastructure
}
state_market_access = {
	value = 0
	add = market_access
}

max_building_financial_center_by_number_in_market = {
	value = var:gdp_view_fc 
	divide = building_financial_num
}

	value = target_supply_mutual_fund_price
	subtract = total_cost_fcc  
}

	value = capital.gdp #target_supply_mutual_fund
	multiply = 250
}

 		}

country_indice_reference_currency = {
	value = 1
	every_country = {
		limit = {
			has_modifier = global_financial_power
		}
		add = country_indice
	}
}
ratio_with_country_indice_reference_currency = {
	value = country_indice
	divide = country_indice_reference_currency
}
ratio_with_country_indice_reference_currency = {
	value = country_indice
	divide = country_indice_reference_currency
}
num_company = {
	value = 0.1
	every_company = {
		add = 1
	}
}
prosperity_company = {
	value = 0
	every_company = {
		add = prosperity
	}
}
prosperity_by_company = {
	value = prosperity_company
	divide = num_company
	divide = 8 #rapporter sur 25
}
investor_massive_capital_loss = {
	value = 0
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:financial_crash = 1
			var:country_indice_value_dif_01 < 0
		}
		add = investment_pool
		multiply = var:country_indice_value_dif_01
	}
}
pop_capital_loss = {
	value = 0
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:economic_crisis = 1
			var:country_indice_value_dif_01 < 0
		}
		add = pop_savings
		multiply = var:country_indice_value_dif_01
	}
}
prosperity_100 = {
	value = prosperity
}

# ██╔════╝██╔══██╗██╔════╝██╔══██╗██║╚══██╔══╝    ██╔══██╗██╔══██╗╚══██╔══╝██║████╗  ██║██╔════╝
# ██║     ██████╔╝█████╗  ██║  ██║██║   ██║       ██████╔╝███████║   ██║   ██║██╔██╗ ██║██║  ███╗
# ██║     ██╔══██╗██╔══╝  ██║  ██║██║   ██║       ██╔══██╗██╔══██║   ██║   ██║██║╚██╗██║██║   ██║
# ╚██████╗██║  ██║███████╗██████╔╝██║   ██║       ██║  ██║██║  ██║   ██║   ██║██║ ╚████║╚██████╔╝
#  ╚═════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚══════╝╚═════╝ ╚═╝   ╚═╝       ╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝   ╚═╝   ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═══╝ ╚═════╝

country_credit_pondered_mean = {
	value = 0

	if = {
		limit = {
			global_country_ranking = 1
			not = {
				is_player = yes
			}
		}
		add = 10
	}

	if = {
		limit = {
			has_modifier = has_central_bank
			#global_country_ranking > 1
			or  = {
				and  = {
					global_country_ranking > 1
					global_country_ranking < 50
				}
				is_player = yes
			}
		}

		value = country_credit_score
		divide = 31
		add = institution_economic_central_bank_lvl

		#is_at_war
		if = {
			limit  = {
				is_at_war = yes
			}
			multiply = is_at_war_years_pulse_malus
		}
		#taking_loans
		if = {
			limit  = {
				taking_loans = yes
			}
			multiply = 0.75
		}
		#credit_rating_national_debt_compared_gdp
		if = {
			limit  = {
				country_credit_rating_national_debt_compared_gdp = 0
			}
			multiply = country_credit_rating_national_debt_compared_gdp_malus_100
		}
	}

	#<50 and no Bc
	if = {
		limit = {
			global_country_ranking < 50
			not = {
				has_modifier = has_central_bank
			}
		}
		add = 4
	}
	#>= 50
	if = {
		limit = {
			global_country_ranking >= 50
			global_country_ranking < 100
			not = {
				has_modifier = has_central_bank
			}
		}
		add = 3
	}
	#>= 100
	if = {
		limit = {
			global_country_ranking >= 100
			global_country_ranking < 150
			not = {
				has_modifier = has_central_bank
			}
		}
		add = 2
	}
	#>= 150
	if = {
		limit = {
			global_country_ranking >= 150
			not = {
				has_modifier = has_central_bank
			}
		}
		add = 1
	}
}
country_credit_score = {
	value = 0

	if = {
		limit = {
			has_modifier = has_central_bank
		}

		add = { #4 x 1 = 4
			add = country_credit_country_rank #40
			multiply = 4
		}

		add = { #2 x 8 = 16
			add = country_credit_rating_ratio_gdp_per_capital #20
			add = country_credit_rating_GDP_grow #20

			add = country_credit_rating_money_value #20
			add = country_credit_rating_inflation #20

			add = country_credit_rating_ratio_with_national_capacity_reference_currency #20
			add = country_credit_rating_ratio_with_country_indice_reference_currency #20
			add = country_credit_rating_national_debt_compared_gdp #20

			add = country_credit_rating_is_losing_power_rank #20

			multiply = 2
		}

		#autre 11
		add = country_credit_rating_sol #10
		add = country_credit_rating_literacy_rate  #10
		add = country_credit_rating_infamy #10
		add = country_credit_rating_government_legitimacy #10

		add = country_credit_rating_army_size #10
		add = country_credit_rating_navy_size #10

		add = country_credit_rating_government_wage_level_value #10
		add = country_credit_rating_military_wage_level_value #10
		add = country_credit_rating_tax_level_value #10

		add = country_credit_rating_radical_fraction #10
		add = country_credit_rating_loyalist_fraction #10
	}
	if = {
		limit = {
			not = {
				has_modifier = has_central_bank
			}
			not = {
				country_rank >= rank_value:decentralized_power
			}
		}
		add = 25
	}
	if = {
		limit = {
			country_rank = rank_value:decentralized_power
		}
		add = 1
	}
}
country_credit_country_rank = {
	value = 0
	min = 0

	if = {
		limit  = {
			global_country_ranking <= 5
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			global_country_ranking <= 10
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			global_country_ranking <= 15
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			global_country_ranking <= 20
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			global_country_ranking <= 25
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			global_country_ranking <= 30
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			global_country_ranking <= 35
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			global_country_ranking <= 40
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			global_country_ranking <= 45
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			global_country_ranking <= 50
		}
		add = 1
	}
}
country_credit_rating_is_losing_power_rank = {
	value = 0
	min = 0

	if = {
		limit  = {
			is_losing_power_rank = no
		}
		add = 10
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			is_losing_power_rank = yes
		}
		add = 0
	}
}

	if = {
		limit  = {
			infamy <= 60
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			infamy <= 50
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			infamy <= 40
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			infamy <= 30
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			infamy <= 20
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			infamy <= 10
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			infamy = 0
		}
		add = 1
	}

}

national_debt_allowed_relative_gdp = {
	value = 0

	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:country_credit_note_fixe = 10
			var:country_credit_note_fixe >= 9
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:country_credit_note_fixe < 9
			var:country_credit_note_fixe >= 8
		}
		add = 0.90

	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:country_credit_note_fixe < 8
			var:country_credit_note_fixe >= 7
		}
		add = 0.80

	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:country_credit_note_fixe < 7
			var:country_credit_note_fixe >= 6
		}
		add = 0.70

	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:country_credit_note_fixe < 6
			var:country_credit_note_fixe >= 5
		}
		add = 0.60

	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:country_credit_note_fixe < 5
			var:country_credit_note_fixe >= 4
		}
		add = 0.50
	}
}
country_credit_rating_national_debt_compared_gdp_malus_100 = {
	value = 1

	if = {
		limit  = {
			country_credit_rating_national_debt_compared_gdp = 0
			national_debt_compared_gdp > 1
			not = {
				national_debt_compared_gdp = 0
			}
		}
		divide = national_debt_compared_gdp
	}
}
country_credit_rating_national_debt_compared_gdp_malus_100_on_interest_rate = {
	value = 1
	if = {
		limit  = {
			not = {
				country_credit_rating_national_debt_compared_gdp_malus_100 = 0
			}
		}
		divide = country_credit_rating_national_debt_compared_gdp_malus_100
	}
}

# Economic Sentiment Index

########################################################################################################################################
########################################################################################################################################
########################################################################################################################################
########################################################################################################################################

economic_sentiment_index_base_JE_fixe = {
    value = var:economic_sentiment_index_base_JE_fixe
}

economic_sentiment_index_base_JE = {
    value = {
		add = {
			add = economic_sentiment_index_base_10 
			subtract = 0.5
		}
		multiply = 10
	} 
}
 
economic_sentiment_index_base_10 = {
	value = economic_sentiment_index
	divide = 100 
}
 
#Bonus
economic_sentiment_index = {
	value = 0
 
	if = {
		limit = {
			has_financial_center = yes
		}
		
		#15 -> 15 x 1 = 15
		add = economic_sentiment_index_base_rate_1_5

		#10 -> 10 x 2 = 20
		add = economic_sentiment_index_stock_market_performance #10
		add = economic_sentiment_index_investement_pool_ratio #10 

		#7.5 -> 7.5 x 2 = 15  
		add =  country_credit_rating_tax_level_value_0_75
		add =  country_credit_rating_national_debt_compared_gdp_0_75

		#10 -> 10 x 10 = 50 
		add =  country_credit_rating_ratio_gdp_per_capital_0_5
		add =  country_credit_rating_GDP_grow_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_money_value_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_inflation_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_ratio_with_national_capacity_reference_currency_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_ratio_with_country_indice_reference_currency_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_infamy_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_government_legitimacy_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_government_wage_level_value_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_military_wage_level_value_0_5 
	}  
 
	if = {
		limit = {
			#is_player = yes
			always = yes
		}
  
		#is_at_war_monthly_pulse
		if = {
			limit = {
				or  = {
					is_at_war = yes
					var:is_at_war_monthly_pulse > 0
				}
			}
			subtract = var:is_at_war_monthly_pulse
		} 
		#is_in_revolution_monthly_pulse
		if = {
			limit = {
				or  = {
					is_at_war = yes
					var:is_in_revolution_monthly_pulse > 0
				}
			}
			subtract = var:is_in_revolution_monthly_pulse
		} 
		#maximum_number_companies_exceeded_monthly_pulse
		if = {
			limit = {
				or  = {
					is_at_war = yes
					var:maximum_number_companies_exceeded_monthly_pulse > 0
				}
			}
			subtract = var:maximum_number_companies_exceeded_monthly_pulse
		} 
	}  
	#(Multiplicator) country_indice_underperformance 
	if = {
		limit = {
			country_indice_underperformance < 1
		}
		multiply = country_indice_underperformance
	} 
	#(Multiplicator) country_in_crisis
	if = {
		limit = {
			or  = {
				has_modifier = declared_bankruptcy
				has_modifier = currency_crisis_country
				has_modifier = central_bank_bankruptcy_country
				has_modifier = financial_crash_country
				has_modifier = economic_crisis_country
			}
		}
		multiply = 0.5
	}  
}  
economic_sentiment_index_no_malus = {
	value = 0 
	if = {
		limit = {
			has_financial_center = yes
		} 

		#15 -> 15 x 1 = 15
		add = economic_sentiment_index_base_rate_1_5

		#10 -> 10 x 2 = 20
		add = economic_sentiment_index_stock_market_performance #10
		add = economic_sentiment_index_investement_pool_ratio #10 

		#7.5 -> 7.5 x 2 = 15  
		add =  country_credit_rating_tax_level_value_0_75
		add =  country_credit_rating_national_debt_compared_gdp_0_75

		#10 -> 10 x 10 = 50 
		add =  country_credit_rating_ratio_gdp_per_capital_0_5
		add =  country_credit_rating_GDP_grow_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_money_value_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_inflation_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_ratio_with_national_capacity_reference_currency_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_ratio_with_country_indice_reference_currency_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_infamy_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_government_legitimacy_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_government_wage_level_value_0_5
		add = country_credit_rating_military_wage_level_value_0_5 
	}    
}   
economic_sentiment_index_investement_pool_ratio = {
	value = 0
	min = 0

	if = {
		limit  = {
			private_bank_funds_pourcent <= 0.4
		}
		add = 2
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			private_bank_funds_pourcent <=  0.3
		}
		add = 2
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			private_bank_funds_pourcent <=  0.2
		}
		add = 2
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			private_bank_funds_pourcent <=  0.1
		}
		add = 2
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			private_bank_funds_pourcent <= 0
		}
		add = 2
	}
}

		add = 1

	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:country_indice_value_dif_01 >= 0.06
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:country_indice_value_dif_01 >= 0.05
		}

	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:country_indice_value_dif_01 >= 0.04
		}
		add = 1

		}

economic_sentiment_index_base_rate = {
    value = 0
	min = 0

    if = {
        limit = { base_rate_percentage_decimal <= 1 }
        add = 1
    }
    if = {
        limit = { base_rate_percentage_decimal <= 2 }
        add = 1
    }
    if = {
        limit = { base_rate_percentage_decimal <= 3 }
        add = 1
    }
    if = {
        limit = { base_rate_percentage_decimal <= 4 }
        add = 1
    }
    if = {
        limit = { base_rate_percentage_decimal <= 5 }
        add = 1
    }
    if = {
        limit = { base_rate_percentage_decimal <= 6 }
        add = 1
    }
    if = {
        limit = { base_rate_percentage_decimal <= 7 }
        add = 1
    }
    if = {
        limit = { base_rate_percentage_decimal <= 8 }
        add = 1
    }
    if = {
        limit = { base_rate_percentage_decimal <= 9 }
        add = 1
    } 
    if = {
        limit = { base_rate_percentage_decimal < 10 }
        add = 1
    } 
} 

#Malus
is_at_war_years_pulse_malus = {
    value = {
        add = 1                               # base = 1
        subtract = {                          # on soustrait (counter/5)*0.5
            add = {
                add = var:is_at_war_years_pulse
                divide = 5
                multiply = 0.5
            }
        }
    }
}
economic_sentiment_index_malus_factor = {
	value = 0 
    if = { 
        limit = { 
            economic_sentiment_index_base_JE_fixe < 0
        } 
		value = { 
			add = economic_sentiment_index_base_JE_fixe
			divide = -5
		}
    }
}  
country_in_crisis = {
	value = 0
	if = {
		limit = {
			not  = {
				or  = {
					has_modifier = declared_bankruptcy
					has_modifier = currency_crisis_country
					has_modifier = central_bank_bankruptcy_country
					has_modifier = financial_crash_country
					has_modifier = economic_crisis_country
				}
			}
		}
		add = 1
	} 
	if = {
		limit = {
			or  = {
				has_modifier = declared_bankruptcy
				has_modifier = currency_crisis_country
				has_modifier = central_bank_bankruptcy_country
				has_modifier = financial_crash_country
				has_modifier = economic_crisis_country
			}
		}
		add = 0.5
	}  
}  
country_indice_underperformance = {
	value = 0
	if = {
		limit = {
			var:country_indice_value_dif_01 >= 0
		}
		add = 1
	} 
	if = {
		limit = {
			var:country_indice_value_dif_01 < 0
		}
		add = 1
		add = var:country_indice_value_dif_01 
	}  
}  
country_max_companies_var = {
	value = 0 
    add = root.modifier:country_max_companies_add 
	floor = yes
}  
num_company_var = {
	value = 0 
    add = num_company 
	floor = yes
}  
maximum_number_companies_exceeded_monthly_pulse = {
	value = 0 
    add = country_max_companies_var
	subtract = num_company_var #nmbre de compagny actuel 
}

# ███████╗████████╗ ██████╗  ██████╗██╗  ██╗██████╗ ██╗██╗     ██╗███╗   ██╗ ██████╗
# ██╔════╝╚══██╔══╝██╔═══██╗██╔════╝██║ ██╔╝██╔══██╗██║██║     ██║████╗  ██║██╔════╝
# ███████╗   ██║   ██║   ██║██║     █████╔╝ ██████╔╝██║██║     ██║██╔██╗ ██║██║  ███╗
# ╚════██║   ██║   ██║   ██║██║     ██╔═██╗ ██╔═══╝ ██║██║     ██║██║╚██╗██║██║   ██║
# ███████║   ██║   ╚██████╔╝╚██████╗██║  ██╗██║     ██║███████╗██║██║ ╚████║╚██████╔╝
# ╚══════╝   ╚═╝    ╚═════╝  ╚═════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝     ╚═╝╚══════╝╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═══╝ ╚═════╝
#
# ███████╗██╗███╗   ██╗ █████╗ ███╗   ██╗ ██████╗██╗ █████╗ ██╗         ██████╗ ██████╗
# ██╔════╝██║████╗  ██║██╔══██╗████╗  ██║██╔════╝██║██╔══██╗██║         ██╔══██╗██╔══██╗
# █████╗  ██║██╔██╗ ██║███████║██╔██╗ ██║██║     ██║███████║██║         ██████╔╝██║  ██║
# ██╔══╝  ██║██║╚██╗██║██╔══██║██║╚██╗██║██║     ██║██╔══██║██║         ██╔═══╝ ██║  ██║
# ██║     ██║██║ ╚████║██║  ██║██║ ╚████║╚██████╗██║██║  ██║███████╗    ██║     ██████╔╝
# ╚═╝     ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═══╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═══╝ ╚═════╝╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚══════╝    ╚═╝     ╚═════╝

#bond
bond_market_goods_sell_orders = {
	value = {
		add = market.mg:bond.market_goods_sell_orders
	}
}
bond_market_goods_buy_orders = {
	value = {
		add = market.mg:bond.market_goods_buy_orders
	}
}
bond_market_goods_delta = {
	value = bond_market_goods_sell_orders
	subtract = bond_market_goods_buy_orders
}
stockpiling_bond_var_1 = {
	value = 0
}
releasing_bond_var_1 = {
	value = 0
}
stockpiling_bond_var_state = {
	value = 0
	add  = {
		every_scope_state = {
			if = {
				limit = {
					has_modifier = financial_center_historic_place
					is_incorporated = yes
				}
				add = var:stockpiling_bond_var_state_1
			}
		}
	}
}

#manufacture_stock
manufacture_stock_market_goods_sell_orders = {
	value = {
		add = market.mg:manufacture_stock.market_goods_sell_orders
	}
}
manufacture_stock_market_goods_buy_orders = {
	value = {
		add = market.mg:manufacture_stock.market_goods_buy_orders
	}
}
manufacture_stock_market_goods_delta = {
	value = manufacture_stock_market_goods_sell_orders
	subtract = manufacture_stock_market_goods_buy_orders
}
stockpiling_manufacture_stock_var_state = {
	value = 0
	add  = {
		every_scope_state = {
			if = {
				limit = {
					has_modifier = financial_center_historic_place
					is_incorporated = yes
				}
				add = var:stockpiling_manufacture_stock_var_state_1
			}
		}
	}
}
manufacture_stock_by_price_in_gold = {
	value = stockpiling_manufacture_stock_var_state
	multiply = manufacture_stock_price_in_gold
}
manufacture_stock_price_in_gold = {
	value = manufacture_stock_price 
	if = {
		limit = {
			has_law = law_type:law_silver_standard
		}
		multiply = money_value_silver_standard_in_gold
	}
	if = {
		limit = {
			has_law = law_type:law_bimetallism_standard
		}
		multiply = money_value_bimetallism_standard_in_gold
	}
} 
manufacture_stock_index_in_gold = {
	value = manufacture_stock_by_price_in_gold
}

# ██╔════╝ ██╔════╝████╗  ██║██╔════╝██╔══██╗██╔══██╗██║
# ██║  ███╗█████╗  ██╔██╗ ██║█████╗  ██████╔╝███████║██║
# ██║   ██║██╔══╝  ██║╚██╗██║██╔══╝  ██╔══██╗██╔══██║██║
# ╚██████╔╝███████╗██║ ╚████║███████╗██║  ██║██║  ██║███████╗
#  ╚═════╝ ╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═══╝╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚══════╝
#
# ██╗███╗   ██╗██████╗ ██╗ ██████╗███████╗
# ██║████╗  ██║██╔══██╗██║██╔════╝██╔════╝
# ██║██╔██╗ ██║██║  ██║██║██║     █████╗
# ██║██║╚██╗██║██║  ██║██║██║     ██╔══╝
# ██║██║ ╚████║██████╔╝██║╚██████╗███████╗

# General indice
country_indice = {
	add = bond_market_index
	add = manufacture_stock_index
	add = agricultural_stock_index
	add = mining_stock_index
	add = railroad_stock_index
}
country_indice_in_gold = {
	add = bond_market_index_in_gold 
	add = manufacture_stock_index_in_gold  
	add = agricultural_stock_index_in_gold 
	add = mining_stock_index_in_gold
	add = railroad_stock_index_in_gold
}
stock_market_index = {
	value = var:base_index_value

	max = 100000
}

# bond_indice
bond_price_0 = {
	value = 50
	subtract = {
		value = 50
		multiply = {
			value = 0
			subtract = {
				value = market.mg:bond.market_goods_pricier
				multiply = 50
			}
			divide = 50
		}
	}
	multiply = 0.33 #30%
}
bond_price_brut = {
	value = 50
	subtract = {
		value = 50
		multiply = {
			value = 0
			subtract = {
				value = market.mg:bond.market_goods_pricier
				multiply = 50
			}
			divide = 50
		}
	}
}
bond_price = {
	add = bond_price_brut 
	#add = bond_price_0
	#add = bond_demand_factor 
}
bond_by_price = {
	value = stockpiling_bond_var_state
	multiply = bond_price
}
bond_by_price_in_gold = {
	value = stockpiling_bond_var_state
	multiply = bond_price_in_gold
}
bond_interest_rate_payable = {
	value = stockpiling_bond_var_state
	multiply = bond_price
	multiply = 1 #country_loan_interest_rate
}
bond_price_in_gold = {
	value = bond_price 
	if = {
		limit = {
			has_law = law_type:law_silver_standard
		}
		multiply = money_value_silver_standard_in_gold
	}
	if = {
		limit = {
			has_law = law_type:law_bimetallism_standard
		}
		multiply = money_value_bimetallism_standard_in_gold
	}
}
bond_market_index = {
	value = bond_by_price
}
bond_market_index_in_gold = {
	value = bond_by_price_in_gold
}
total_debt = {
	value = bond_market_index
	add = central_bank_debt # deja à 75% max 25% du coverage -> je monte au max si le pays dois assurer sa valeur mais qu'il ne peut pas les pret etranger sont une soure de regule +++ aevec pour cible 75% de la valeur couvete
} 
total_debt_in_gold = {
	value = 0
	if = {
		limit = {
			has_law = law_type:law_gold_standard
			#no law_gold_exchange_standard
		}
		add = total_debt
	}
	if = {
		limit = {
			has_law = law_type:law_silver_standard
		} 
		add = total_debt
		multiply = silver_to_gold_rate #silver_to_gold_rate
	}
	if = {
		limit = {
			has_law = law_type:law_bimetallism_standard
		} 
		add = total_debt
		#multiply = bimetallic_rate_silver_to_gold #silver_to_gold_rate
	}
}
 
remaining_debt = {
	value = total_debt_in_gold
	subtract = gold_loaned_to_central_bank
	min = 0
}
remaining_debt_90 = {
	value = total_debt_in_gold
	multiply = 0.9
}
total_debt_80 = {
	value = total_debt_in_gold
	multiply = 0.8
}

bond_demand_factor = {
	value = 33
	multiply = ratio_with_highest_prestige

	max = 33
}
highest_prestige = {
	every_country = {
		limit = {
			global_country_ranking = 1
		}
		add = prestige
	}
}
bond_money_value_factor = {
	value = 33
	multiply = money_value_in_gold #money_value

	max = 33
}

# ███████╗██╗   ██╗██████╗ ██████╗ ██╗  ██╗   ██╗    ██████╗ ███████╗███╗   ███╗ █████╗ ███╗   ██╗██████╗     ███████╗ ██████╗ ██████╗

# ███████╗██║   ██║██████╔╝██████╔╝██║   ╚████╔╝     ██║  ██║█████╗  ██╔████╔██║███████║██╔██╗ ██║██║  ██║    █████╗  ██║   ██║██████╔╝

# ███████║╚██████╔╝██║     ██║     ███████╗██║       ██████╔╝███████╗██║ ╚═╝ ██║██║  ██║██║ ╚████║██████╔╝    ██║     ╚██████╔╝██║  ██║
# ╚══════╝ ╚═════╝ ╚═╝     ╚═╝     ╚══════╝╚═╝       ╚═════╝ ╚══════╝╚═╝     ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═══╝╚═════╝     ╚═╝      ╚═════╝ ╚═╝  ╚═╝
#
# ███████╗██╗███╗   ██╗ █████╗ ███╗   ██╗ ██████╗██╗ █████╗ ██╗         ██████╗ ██████╗  ██████╗ ██████╗ ██╗   ██╗ ██████╗████████╗

# █████╗  ██║██╔██╗ ██║███████║██╔██╗ ██║██║     ██║███████║██║         ██████╔╝██████╔╝██║   ██║██║  ██║██║   ██║██║        ██║
# ██╔══╝  ██║██║╚██╗██║██╔══██║██║╚██╗██║██║     ██║██╔══██║██║         ██╔═══╝ ██╔══██╗██║   ██║██║  ██║██║   ██║██║        ██║
# ██║     ██║██║ ╚████║██║  ██║██║ ╚████║╚██████╗██║██║  ██║███████╗    ██║     ██║  ██║╚██████╔╝██████╔╝╚██████╔╝╚██████╗   ██║
# ╚═╝     ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═══╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═══╝ ╚═════╝╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚══════╝    ╚═╝     ╚═╝  ╚═╝ ╚═════╝ ╚═════╝  ╚═════╝  ╚═════╝   ╚═╝

############
#bg_financial_centre
############
bg_financial_centre_occupancy = {
	value = 0
	every_scope_building = {
		limit = {
			is_building_group = bg_financial_centre
		}
		add = occupancy
	}
}
bg_financial_centre_occupancy_reverse = {
	value = 1
	if = {
		limit = {
			bg_financial_centre_occupancy < 0.9
			bg_financial_centre_occupancy > 0.1  #à  voire
		}
		add  = {
			add = bg_financial_centre_occupancy
			subtract = 1
			multiply = -1
		}
	}
}
bg_financial_centre_lvl_on_market = {
	value = 0
	every_country = {
		limit = {
		    market.owner = root
			has_modifier = has_financial_center
		}
		add = 1
	}
}
bg_financial_centre_modifier = {
	value = 0
	every_scope_building = {
		limit = {
			is_building_group = bg_financial_centre
		}
		add = country_company_throughput_bonus
	}
}

############
#mutual_fund
############
bond_price_by_demand_fc = {
	value = 0
	add = target_demand_bond_ajusted
	multiply = bond_price_brut
}
manufacture_stock_price_by_demand_fc = {
	value = 0
	add = target_demand_manufacture_stock_ajusted
	multiply = manufacture_stock_price_brut
}
agricultural_stock_price_by_demand_fc = {
	value = 0
	add = target_demand_agricultural_stock_ajusted
	multiply = agricultural_stock_price_brut
}
mining_stock_price_by_demand_fc = {
	value = 0
	add = target_demand_mining_stock_ajusted
	multiply = mining_stock_price_brut
}
railroad_stock_price_by_demand_fc = {
	value = 0
	add = target_demand_railroad_stock_ajusted
	multiply = railroad_stock_price_brut
}
total_cost_fcc = {
	value = 0
	add = bond_price_by_demand_fc
	add = manufacture_stock_price_by_demand_fc
	add = agricultural_stock_price_by_demand_fc
	add = mining_stock_price_by_demand_fc
	add = railroad_stock_price_by_demand_fc
}
base_supply_mutual_fund = {
    value = bg_financial_centre_lvl
    multiply = 1
}
base_supply_mutual_fund = {  
	value = scope:financial_center_scope.modifier:goods_input_bond_add 
}
base_supply_mutual_fund_fix = { 
	value = var:base_demande_bond_fix
}
collateral_quantity_mutual_fund = {
    value = total_cost_fcc
    divide = 250
}
target_supply_mutual_fund = {
    value = collateral_quantity_mutual_fund #quantité à avoir pour assurer le cout des bien
    multiply = 1.5 ##ajuster cette vvaleur pour augmenter prix du bien au dessus de neutralité 
}
total_gain_mf = {
    value = target_supply_mutual_fund  
    multiply = 250  
} 
target_supply_mutual_fund_for_modifier = {
    value = target_supply_mutual_fund
    subtract = base_supply_mutual_fund_fix
    divide = base_supply_mutual_fund_fix
    multiply = 100 
	if = {
		limit = {
			or = {
				is_subject = yes
				not = {
					market.owner = root
				}
			}
		}
		multiply = 0.1
	}
}

fiancial_center_week_balance = {
    value = total_gain_mf  
    subtract = total_cost_fcc  
	multiply = building_financial_num
} 
fiancial_center_week_balance_in_gdp = {
    value = fiancial_center_week_balance  
    multiply = 52  
} 
fiancial_center_week_balance_in_ratio = {
    value = fiancial_center_week_balance_in_gdp
	divide = gdp_var  
} 

speculative_share_1_penality = {
    value = var:speculative_share_1  
	multiply = -1 
}  
speculative_share_2_penality = {
    value = var:speculative_share_2
	multiply = -1 
}  


############
#bond
############
base_demande_bond = {  
	value = scope:financial_center_scope.modifier:goods_input_bond_add 
}
base_demande_bond_fix = { 
	value = var:base_demande_bond_fix
}
target_demand_bond = {
    value = bond_market_goods_sell_orders
    multiply = 1 #ajuster cette vvaleur pour augmenter prix du bien au dessus de neutralité
}
target_demand_bond_ajusted = {
    value = target_demand_bond
    subtract = market.mg:bond.market_goods_exports
	divide = building_financial_num #Je divise la quantité dans le marché à ciblé en fonction du nombre de FC pour un equilibrage globale ---------------> division par zero possible  

	if = {
		limit = {
			or = {
				is_subject = yes
				not = {
					market.owner = root
				}
			}
		}
		multiply = 0.05
	}
	if = { limit = { has_modifier = speculative_share_modifier_2 } multiply = 0.75 }
	if = { limit = { has_modifier = speculative_share_modifier_3 } multiply = 0.5 }
	if = { limit = { has_modifier = speculative_share_modifier_4 } multiply = 0.25 }

	min = 0 
}
target_demand_bond_for_modifier = { 
	value = 0 
	value = target_demand_bond_ajusted
	subtract = base_demande_bond_fix
	divide = base_demande_bond_fix
	multiply = 100 
	
	max = 25000
}  
bond_market_goods_sell_orders_ratio = {
    value = bond_market_goods_sell_orders
	multiply = financial_product_by_trade_route
}

		limit = {
			or = {
				is_subject = yes

					market.owner = root

			}
		}
		multiply = 0.05

	if = { limit = { has_modifier = speculative_share_modifier_3 } multiply = 0.5 }
	if = { limit = { has_modifier = speculative_share_modifier_4 } multiply = 0.25 }

building_trade_center_lvl = {
    value = 0
    any_scope_building = {
        limit = {
            is_building_type = building_financial_district
			#has_building = building_railway

        }
		add = level

    }
}
building_financial_district_lvl = {
    value = 0
    every_scope_building = {
        limit = {
            is_building_type = building_financial_district
        }
        add = level
    }
}
building_railway_lvl_X = { #mee donnee si unn bbanntimeent lamhbda eest détennue à une part
    value = 0
	if = {
		limit = {
			any_scope_building = {
				level > 0
				private_ownership_fraction > 0
				is_building_type = building_railway
			}
		}
		add = 1
	}
}

sell_limit_var_0 = {
	value = 1000000
	if = {
		limit = {
			country_rank = rank_value:great_power
		}
		value = 10000000
	}
	if = {
		limit = {
			country_rank = rank_value:major_power
		}
		value = 5000000
	}
}

#grain

grain_price = {
	value = 20
	subtract = {
		value = 20
		multiply = {
			value = 0
			subtract = {
				value = market.mg:grain.market_goods_pricier
				multiply = 20
			}
			divide = 20
		}
	}
}

			value = 0
			subtract = {
				value = market.mg:rubber.market_goods_pricier
				multiply = 40
			}
			divide = 40
		}
	}
}

# ██╔══██╗██╔═══██╗████╗  ██║██╔══██╗    ██╔══██╗    ██╔════╝██║   ██║██╔══██╗██╔══██╗██╔══██╗██║████╗ ████║██╔════╝██╔══██╗
# ██████╔╝██║   ██║██╔██╗ ██║██║  ██║    ███████║    ███████╗██║   ██║██████╔╝██████╔╝██████╔╝██║██╔████╔██║█████╗  ██████╔╝
# ██╔══██╗██║   ██║██║╚██╗██║██║  ██║    ██╔══██║    ╚════██║██║   ██║██╔═══╝ ██╔═══╝ ██╔══██╗██║██║╚██╔╝██║██╔══╝  ██╔══██╗
# ██████╔╝╚██████╔╝██║ ╚████║██████╔╝    ██║  ██║    ███████║╚██████╔╝██║     ██║     ██║  ██║██║██║ ╚═╝ ██║███████╗██║  ██║
# ╚═════╝  ╚═════╝ ╚═╝  ╚═══╝╚═════╝     ╚═╝  ╚═╝    ╚══════╝ ╚═════╝ ╚═╝     ╚═╝     ╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝╚═╝     ╚═╝╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝

###########################################################################################################################################################################################
###########################################################################################################################################################################################
###########################################################################################################################################################################################
###########################################################################################################################################################################################

price_bond = {
	value = player.var:bond_quantity
	multiply = bond_price
}
price_bond_in_currency = {
	value = player.var:bond_quantity
	multiply = bond_price

	if = {
		limit = {
			player.var:bond_in_on = 1
		}
		divide = money_value
	}
}
price_bond_in_currency_for_gui = {
	value = scope:buyer.var:bond_quantity
	multiply = bond_price

	if = {
		limit = {
			scope:buyer.var:bond_in_on = 1
		}
		divide = money_value
	}
}

		if = {
			limit = {
				has_law = law_type:law_spe_yuan_currency
			}
			player = {
				every_scope_state = {
					if = {
						limit = {
							has_modifier = central_bank_historic_place
						}
						add = var:stockpiling_spe_yuan_state_1
						add = var:stockpiling_spe_yuan_reserve_currency_state_1
					}
				}
			}
		}
		#spe_zloti
		if = {
			limit = {
				has_law = law_type:law_spe_zloti_currency
			}
			player = {
				every_scope_state = {
					if = {
						limit = {
							has_modifier = central_bank_historic_place
						}
						add = var:stockpiling_spe_zloti_state_1
						add = var:stockpiling_spe_zloti_reserve_currency_state_1
					}
				}
			}
		}
		#thaler_hannoveraner_thaler
		if = {
			limit = {
				has_law = law_type:law_thaler_hannoveraner_thaler_currency
			}
			player = {
				every_scope_state = {
					if = {
						limit = {
							has_modifier = central_bank_historic_place
						}
						add = var:stockpiling_thaler_hannoveraner_thaler_state_1
						add = var:stockpiling_thaler_hannoveraner_thaler_reserve_currency_state_1
					}
				}
			}
		}
		#thaler_prussian_thaler
		if = {
			limit = {
				has_law = law_type:law_thaler_prussian_thaler_currency
			}
			player = {
				every_scope_state = {
					if = {
						limit = {
							has_modifier = central_bank_historic_place
						}
						add = var:stockpiling_thaler_prussian_thaler_state_1
						add = var:stockpiling_thaler_prussian_thaler_reserve_currency_state_1
					}
				}
			}
		}
		#thaler_saxon_thaler
		if = {
			limit = {
				has_law = law_type:law_thaler_saxon_thaler_currency
			}
			player = {
				every_scope_state = {
					if = {

					}
				}

		}
	}

interconnected_crises = {
	value = 0
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:currency_crisis = 1
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:economic_crisis = 1
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:financial_crash = 1
		}
		add = 1
	}
	if = {
		limit  = {
			var:country_bankruptcy = 1
		}
		add = 1
	}
}

			has_modifier = interest_from_foreign_debt_investment
		}
		add = var:ai_interest_calculated_8
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			is_set = var:ai_interest_calculated_9
			has_modifier = interest_from_foreign_debt_investment
		}
		add = var:ai_interest_calculated_9
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			is_set = var:ai_interest_calculated_10
			has_modifier = interest_from_foreign_debt_investment
		}
		add = var:ai_interest_calculated_10
	}
}

#gold
ai_central_bank_gold_loaned_1 = {
	every_in_list = {
		variable = central_bank_debt_buyer_list_1
		add = var:ai_total_bond_value_1
		if  = {
			limit  = {
				var:total_bond_value_1 > 0
			}
			add = var:total_bond_value_1
		}
	}
}

ai_privat_bank_interest_calculated_14_from_list = {
	value = 0
	#company_BasicBank

		add = owner.var:ai_privat_bank_interest_calculated_25
	}
	#company_BancoDeValparaiso
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			is_company_type = company_type:company_BancoDeValparaiso
		}
		add = owner.var:ai_privat_bank_interest_calculated_25
	}
	#company_BancoNacionalDeBolivia
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			is_company_type = company_type:company_BancoNacionalDeBolivia
		}
		add = owner.var:ai_privat_bank_interest_calculated_25
	}
	#company_BancoRepublicaColombia
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			is_company_type = company_type:company_BancoRepublicaColombia
		}
		add = owner.var:ai_privat_bank_interest_calculated_25
	}
	#company_BancoCentralDeVenezuela
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			is_company_type = company_type:company_BancoCentralDeVenezuela
		}
		add = owner.var:ai_privat_bank_interest_calculated_25
	}
	#company_BancoEspanolDeLaHabana
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			is_company_type = company_type:company_BancoEspanolDeLaHabana
		}
		add = owner.var:ai_privat_bank_interest_calculated_25
	}
	#company_BancoCentralDelUruguay
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			is_company_type = company_type:company_BancoCentralDelUruguay
		}
		add = owner.var:ai_privat_bank_interest_calculated_25
	}
	#company_BancoNacionalDelParaguay
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			is_company_type = company_type:company_BancoNacionalDelParaguay
		}
		add = owner.var:ai_privat_bank_interest_calculated_25
	}
	#company_BankSBoBS
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			is_company_type = company_type:company_BankSBoBS
		}
		add = owner.var:ai_privat_bank_interest_calculated_25
	}
}

bond_quantity_scripted = {
	value = 0


	# cpacité d'emprunt  par ligne  de   10% de la reserve
	#consomme 70% de  la ressserve

	#vérifit si le remaining_debt  est inferieur à gold_reserves_10 si  cela est  le  cas  alors  la  valeur  est  de remaining_debt

	if  = {
		limit  = {
			scope:seller.remaining_debt < gold_reserves_10
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = scope:seller.remaining_debt
			divide = scope:seller.bond_price
		}
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			scope:seller.remaining_debt > gold_reserves_10
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = gold_reserves_var_10
			divide = scope:seller.bond_price
		}
	}
}
bond_quantity_scripted_all = {
	value = 0
	add = {
		value = 0
		add = scope:seller.central_bank_debt
		divide = scope:seller.bond_price
	}
}
gold_loan_preview  = {
	value = bond_quantity_scripted
	multiply = scope:seller.bond_price
}
bond_quantity_scripted_test = {
	value = 0
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			gold_reserves > gold_reserves_10
			gold_reserves < gold_reserves_20
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = gold_reserves_var_02
			#divide = scope:seller.bond_price
		}
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			gold_reserves > gold_reserves_20
			gold_reserves < gold_reserves_30
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = gold_reserves_var_03
			#divide = scope:seller.bond_price
		}
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			gold_reserves > gold_reserves_30
			gold_reserves < gold_reserves_40
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = gold_reserves_var_04
			#divide = scope:seller.bond_price
		}
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			gold_reserves > gold_reserves_40
			gold_reserves < gold_reserves_50
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = gold_reserves_var_05
			#divide = scope:seller.bond_price
		}
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			gold_reserves > gold_reserves_50
			gold_reserves < gold_reserves_60
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = gold_reserves_var_06
			#divide = scope:seller.bond_price
		}
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			gold_reserves > gold_reserves_60
			gold_reserves < gold_reserves_70
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = gold_reserves_var_07
			#divide = scope:seller.bond_price
		}
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			gold_reserves > gold_reserves_70
			gold_reserves < gold_reserves_80
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = gold_reserves_var_08
			#divide = scope:seller.bond_price
		}
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			gold_reserves > gold_reserves_80
			gold_reserves < gold_reserves_90
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = gold_reserves_var_09
			#divide = scope:seller.bond_price
		}
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			gold_reserves > gold_reserves_90
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = gold_reserves_var_10
			#divide = scope:seller.bond_price
		}
	}
}

}

	add = var:interest_per_month_calculated_3
	add = var:interest_per_month_calculated_4
	add = var:interest_per_month_calculated_5
	add = var:interest_per_month_calculated_6
	add = var:interest_per_month_calculated_7

	add = var:ai_interest_per_month_calculated_3
	add = var:ai_interest_per_month_calculated_4
	add = var:ai_interest_per_month_calculated_5
	add = var:ai_interest_per_month_calculated_6

}

quantite_de_bon_pour_payer_toute_la_dette = {
	value = 0
	add = remaining_debt
	divide = bond_price_in_gold
}

bond_quantity_scripted_privat_bank = {
	value = 0

	# cpacité d'emprunt  par ligne  de   10% de la reserve
	#consomme 70% de  la ressserve

	#vérifit si le remaining_debt  est inferieur à gold_reserves_10 si  cela est  le  cas  alors  la  valeur  est  de remaining_debt

	#achat total si en dessous du seil direct
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			scope:seller.remaining_debt < private_bank_funds_25
			scope:seller.remaining_debt > 0 #si inf à 0 ou 0 alors bond_quantity_scripted_privat_bank = 0
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = scope:seller.remaining_debt
			divide = scope:seller.bond_price_in_gold
		}
	}
	if  = {
		limit  = {
			scope:seller.remaining_debt > private_bank_funds_25
			private_bank_funds_25 > 0 #si inf à 0 ou 0 alors bond_quantity_scripted_privat_bank = 0
		}
		add = {
			value = 0
			add = private_bank_funds_25
			divide = scope:seller.bond_price_in_gold
		}
	}
}

position_regulator = {
	value = 0
 	add = var:position_regulator
 	add = total_privat_bank
}

	value = 0
	if = {
		limit = { 
			any_scope_state = {
				has_building = building_financial_centre 
			} 
		}
		add = 1
	}
}

leading_producer_of_oil = {
	value = 0
	if = {
		limit = { 
			leading_producer_of = g:oil
		}
		add = 1
	}
}
